        <abstract>
            <p>A draft letter [but sent in the original state by Emma Darwin]. Approves of FJW’s notice of his views.</p>
            <p>CD has slightly revised parts in view of both approving and disapproving critics, but still remains convinced about his fundamental notions.</p>
        </abstract>
